{% comment %}
  CUSTOM · Fast Wear — second of the two "features" sections (custom-features-intro is
  the first). Same visual language: black scheme-4, orange #fb6e06, stroke icons.
  Content fully hardcoded (settings: []), copy locale-gated IT/EN/FR per decision 024.

  Every surface in here stays pure black on purpose. The supplied step images are shot
  on #000 and cannot be keyed (a black shoe on a black background), so any panel behind
  them that is even slightly lighter would show each one as a black rectangle. The card
  look comes from hairline borders and rounded corners instead of a fill. See decision 033.
{% endcomment %}
{{ 'custom-features-fastwear.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign is_en = false
  assign is_fr = false
  if request.locale.iso_code == 'en'
    assign is_en = true
  elsif request.locale.iso_code == 'fr'
    assign is_fr = true
  endif
-%}

<div class="custom-features-fastwear color-scheme-4 gradient">
  <div class="custom-features-fastwear__inner page-width">
    <div class="custom-features-fastwear__intro">
      <p class="custom-features-fastwear__overline">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          FAST WEAR TECHNOLOGY
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          TECHNOLOGIE FAST WEAR
        {%- else -%}
          TECNOLOGIA FAST WEAR
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>

      <h2 class="custom-features-fastwear__heading">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          SLIP IN.<br>STEP DOWN.<br>GO.<br>IN 2 SECONDS.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          ENFILEZ.<br>DESCENDEZ.<br>PARTEZ.<br>EN 2 SECONDES.
        {%- else -%}
          INFILA.<br>SCENDI.<br>VIA.<br>IN 2 SECONDI.
        {%- endif -%}
      </h2>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      The shoe sits on the LEFT, where the design puts it on the right. The photo is used
      as shot, not mirrored: it carries the DrKAMPES heel logo and a MADE IN ITALY stamp,
      and a horizontal flip renders both backwards. As shot, the toe points right — into
      the copy — which is the same inward-facing composition the design gets by flipping
      the shoe to the right-hand side.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <img
      src="{{ 'fastwear-hero.jpg' | asset_url }}"
      alt=""
      width="1500"
      height="1108"
      class="custom-features-fastwear__hero-media"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >

    <div class="custom-features-fastwear__body">
      <p>
        {%- if is_en -%}
          The Fast Wear system transforms the way you put on safety shoes. The reinforced, flexible heel collapses as you slide your foot in and springs back into place in an instant, giving you stability and support all day long.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          Le système Fast Wear révolutionne la façon d'enfiler les chaussures de sécurité. Le talon renforcé et flexible s'affaisse quand vous glissez le pied et revient en place en un instant, garantissant stabilité et maintien toute la journée.
        {%- else -%}
          Il sistema Fast Wear rivoluziona il modo di indossare le scarpe antinfortunistiche. Il tallone rinforzato e flessibile collassa quando infili il piede e torna in posizione in un attimo, garantendo stabilità e sostegno per tutta la giornata.
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>
      <p class="custom-features-fastwear__kicker">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          Zero wasted time. Maximum efficiency.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          Zéro perte de temps. Efficacité maximale.
        {%- else -%}
          Zero perdite di tempo. Massima efficienza.
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      An <ol>, not a <ul>: these are ordered steps, and the order is the whole point. The
      orange numerals are the visual echo of that order, so they are aria-hidden — the
      list element already conveys the sequence to a screen reader, and reading "one one
      infila" would be a stutter.

      The step photos need no mask, unlike the hero shot above: they are already on pure
      black and so is the card behind them, so the edges have nothing to dissolve into.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <ol class="custom-features-fastwear__steps" role="list">
      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__step">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        <div class="custom-features-fastwear__step-text">
          <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__step-title">
            {%- if is_en -%}READY{%- elsif is_fr -%}PRÊTES{%- else -%}PREPARA{%- endif -%}
          </h3>
          <p>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              No laces to tie. The shoe is already waiting for you.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              Aucun lacet à nouer. La chaussure vous attend déjà.
            {%- else -%}
              Nessun laccio da allacciare. La scarpa ti aspetta già pronta.
            {%- endif -%}
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="{{ 'fastwear-step-1.jpg' | asset_url }}"
          alt=""
          width="900"
          height="414"
          class="custom-features-fastwear__step-media"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__step">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        <div class="custom-features-fastwear__step-text">
          <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__step-title">
            {%- if is_en -%}SLIP IN{%- elsif is_fr -%}ENFILEZ{%- else -%}INFILA{%- endif -%}
          </h3>
          <p>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              The heel collapses under your foot and lets you straight in.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              Le talon s'affaisse sous le pied et vous laisse entrer.
            {%- else -%}
              Il tallone collassa sotto il piede e ti lascia entrare.
            {%- endif -%}
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="{{ 'fastwear-step-2.jpg' | asset_url }}"
          alt=""
          width="900"
          height="414"
          class="custom-features-fastwear__step-media"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__step">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        <div class="custom-features-fastwear__step-text">
          <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__step-title">
            {%- if is_en -%}GO{%- elsif is_fr -%}PARTEZ{%- else -%}VIA{%- endif -%}
          </h3>
          <p>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              The heel springs back into place. You are ready to work.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              Le talon revient en place. Vous êtes prêt à travailler.
            {%- else -%}
              Il tallone torna in posizione. Sei pronto a lavorare.
            {%- endif -%}
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="{{ 'fastwear-step-3.jpg' | asset_url }}"
          alt=""
          width="900"
          height="414"
          class="custom-features-fastwear__step-media"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
      </li>
    </ol>

    {%- comment -%}
      The payoff grid. Stroke icons again, coloured by the container via currentColor —
      no fill declared anywhere, or the stroke icons would flood solid (see rules.md).
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <ul class="custom-features-fastwear__benefits" role="list">
      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          {{- 'icon-stopwatch-line.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
        </span>
        <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit-title">
          {%- if is_en -%}SAVE TIME{%- elsif is_fr -%}GAGNEZ DU TEMPS{%- else -%}RISPARMI TEMPO{%- endif -%}
        </h3>
        <p>
          {%- if is_en -%}
            Every single time you put them on.
          {%- elsif is_fr -%}
            À chaque fois que vous les enfilez.
          {%- else -%}
            Ogni volta che le indossi.
          {%- endif -%}
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          {{- 'icon-boot-line.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
        </span>
        <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit-title">
          {%- if is_en -%}TOTAL STABILITY{%- elsif is_fr -%}STABILITÉ TOTALE{%- else -%}STABILITÀ TOTALE{%- endif -%}
        </h3>
        <p>
          {%- if is_en -%}
            A heel that never gives way.
          {%- elsif is_fr -%}
            Un talon qui ne cède jamais.
          {%- else -%}
            Tallone che non cede.
          {%- endif -%}
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          {{- 'icon-refresh-line.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
        </span>
        <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit-title">
          {%- if is_en -%}BUILT TO LAST{%- elsif is_fr -%}DURABLE DANS LE TEMPS{%- else -%}DUREVOLE NEL TEMPO{%- endif -%}
        </h3>
        <p>
          {%- if is_en -%}
            Engineered to go the distance.
          {%- elsif is_fr -%}
            Conçu pour durer.
          {%- else -%}
            Progettato per durare.
          {%- endif -%}
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          {{- 'icon-sock-line.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
        </span>
        <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__benefit-title">
          {%- if is_en -%}INSTANT COMFORT{%- elsif is_fr -%}CONFORT IMMÉDIAT{%- else -%}COMFORT IMMEDIATO{%- endif -%}
        </h3>
        <p>
          {%- if is_en -%}
            No pressure points.
          {%- elsif is_fr -%}
            Aucun point de pression.
          {%- else -%}
            Nessun punto di pressione.
          {%- endif -%}
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "CUSTOM · Fast Wear",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "custom-features-fastwear-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "CUSTOM · Fast Wear"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
